<Layout title="Ian Bragg, Senior Applied AI Engineer">
  <h1>Ian Bragg</h1>
  <p class="tagline">
    Senior applied AI engineer. 11 years of building things that have to actually work in production.
  </p>

  <div class="signals">
    <span class="signal">11 years engineering, 8 years AI/ML</span>
    <span class="signal">AI SME, DEVCOM AvMC Software Assurance</span>
    <span class="signal">CISSP, Active TS/SCI</span>
    <span class="signal">Teach AI capabilities, data literacy, automation</span>
    <span class="signal">Speaks in software-assurance, DevSecOps, AI communities</span>
    <span class="signal">D.Tech., Purdue (in progress)</span>
    <span class="signal">M.S. CS, Georgia Tech (Computational Perception & Robotics)</span>
